OL,3,C'Bionic MP' Craig Mackinlay leaves
OL,4,Coffice ahead of Parliament dissolution
OL,6,FConservative MP Craig Mackinlay is
OL,7,Fleaving his office in Parliament
OL,8,Ftoday, as he serves his last day as an
OL,9,FMP.
OL,11,FThe South Thanet MP decided not to
OL,12,Fstand in the General Election so he
OL,13,Fcould focus on his recovery from
OL,14,Fsepsis.
OL,16,FHe said: "I was a bit like that woman
OL,17,Ffrom Bristol, 'oh no not another one'.
OL,18,FBut we knew one was coming this year.
