OL,3,C'Bionic MP' Craig Mackinlay leaves
OL,4,Coffice ahead of Parliament dissolution
OL,6,F"We expected it later in the year. It
OL,7,Fwas a surprise just about to everyone
OL,8,Fin the house that it came so quickly."
OL,10,FMr Mackinlay had only just returned to
OL,11,Fwork after a nightmare ordeal.
OL,13,FHe was taken to hospital on 28
OL,14,FSeptember and put into a 16-day
OL,15,Finduced coma, with his wife told he
OL,16,Fhad only a 5% chance of survival.
OL,18,FSurgeons subsequently amputated his
OL,19,Fhands and feet in order to save his
OL,20,Flife as sepsis ravaged his body.
