OL,3,C'Bionic MP' Craig Mackinlay leaves
OL,4,Coffice ahead of Parliament dissolution
OL,6,F"Maybe I was kidding myself that I
OL,7,Fwould have been ready in October or
OL,8,FNovember, but at least I had the
OL,9,Fbenefit of a bit of time to do more
OL,10,Frehab, get the hang of these
OL,11,Fprosthetics.
OL,13,F"Given that it was called earlier, I
OL,14,Fhad to make a pretty quick decision
OL,15,Fbecause that's the fair thing to do
OL,16,Ffor my constituents and my party so
OL,17,Fthey can look to a new Conservative."
