OL,3,C'Bionic MP' Craig Mackinlay leaves
OL,4,Coffice ahead of Parliament dissolution
OL,6,FMr Mackinlay has been trying to raise
OL,7,Fawareness of symptoms of sepsis to
OL,8,Fmake sure others make sure to get
OL,9,Fchecked if they feel unwell.
OL,11,FHe continued: "Usually you get a few
OL,12,Fdays to recognise (the symptoms of
OL,13,Fsepsis), I wasn't that fortunate but
OL,14,Fif I can save someone else's limbs or
OL,15,Fsave a life, I see that as a job very
OL,16,Fwell done.
OL,18,F"I'd also like to be working with the
OL,19,FNHS, which has started to an extent,
OL,20,Fon making sure people get appropriate
OL,21,Faesthetics."
